Reusing images from Wikimedia Commons should be easy.


MediaWikiImageSource.php
    Class to retrieve image information from Wikimedia Commons

index.php
    web interface to play around

commonsapi_test.php
    experimental Wikimedia Commons image API by Magnus Manske

Proxy_Request.php
    Proxy Server Support for VuFind. Only needed to in VuFind.
    Source: https://vufind.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/vufind/trunk 

